{"synckey":1608333995,"totalCount":5,"reviews":[{"reviewId":"9949958_7fRk55nzb","review":{"abstract":"假设1978年前一个家族通过勤奋努力或者各种方式积累了大量的财富，但接下来的40年里，后代如果没有能力完成这个财富传承的游戏，家道中落似乎是一种必然，所以财富管理不仅仅是一代人的事，它需要几代人持续的努力。这也许就是我们投资的根本原因。","atUserVids":[],"bookId":"928569","bookVersion":1490813738,"chapterUid":9,"content":"因为通胀，所以需要投资，因为投资，所以新产品新技术新科技，因为效率高，所以通胀。","friendship":0,"htmlContent":"","isPrivate":0,"range":"2069-2187","title":"","type":1,"reviewId":"9949958_7fRk55nzb","userVid":9949958,"topics":[],"createTime":1584233768,"flag":0,"isLike":0,"isReposted":0,"book":{"bookId":"928569","format":"epub","version":465933926,"soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"type":0,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/61/YueWen_928569/s_YueWen_928569.jpg","title":"买入，持有，富有：一名金牛基金经理的投资之路","author":"张可兴","payType":1048577},"chapterIdx":9,"chapterTitle":"守不住财富的储蓄","author":{"userVid":9949958,"name":"孙大年","avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/0u8VlNPjial6zuBqSazyIoM4KHl1W5mYMTMFVibJ387ia62l40PaCryL953jkW76HxzUkloyqTZ1h7VQdobMTgtmf26uLTTSkXR2WWAKuINauU/132","isFollowing":1,"isFollower":1,"isBlacking":0,"isBlackBy":0,"isHide":1,"isV":0,"roleTags":[],"followPromote":"","isDeepV":false,"deepVTitle":"","signature":"","medalInfo":{"id":"M3-0-2000","desc":"阅读天数","title":"阅读天数","levelIndex":2000}}},"likesCount":2},{"reviewId":"9949958_7fRjR1WD2","review":{"abstract":"1930年的1美元，70年后只有0.07美元的购买力。这意味着如果我们不善待财富，“长脚的钱”会随着时间悄然流逝。","atUserVids":[],"bookId":"928569","bookVersion":2010343766,"chapterUid":9,"content":"倒过来看，商品也呈现极大丰富的局面。","friendship":0,"htmlContent":"","isPrivate":0,"range":"792-849","title":"","type":1,"reviewId":"9949958_7fRjR1WD2","userVid":9949958,"topics":[],"createTime":1584233561,"flag":0,"isLike":0,"isReposted":0,"book":{"bookId":"928569","format":"epub","version":465933926,"soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"type":0,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/61/YueWen_928569/s_YueWen_928569.jpg","title":"买入，持有，富有：一名金牛基金经理的投资之路","author":"张可兴","payType":1048577},"chapterIdx":9,"chapterTitle":"守不住财富的储蓄","author":{"userVid":9949958,"name":"孙大年","avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/0u8VlNPjial6zuBqSazyIoM4KHl1W5mYMTMFVibJ387ia62l40PaCryL953jkW76HxzUkloyqTZ1h7VQdobMTgtmf26uLTTSkXR2WWAKuINauU/132","isFollowing":1,"isFollower":1,"isBlacking":0,"isBlackBy":0,"isHide":1,"isV":0,"roleTags":[],"followPromote":"","isDeepV":false,"deepVTitle":"","signature":"","medalInfo":{"id":"M3-0-2000","desc":"阅读天数","title":"阅读天数","levelIndex":2000}}}},{"reviewId":"9949958_7fRjzU1PH","review":{"abstract":"我们研究了A股15年股市历史，以及港股、美股几十年甚至上百年的股票历史，之后对股市的运行逻辑和股票的涨跌逻辑进行了深刻的剖析。","atUserVids":[],"bookId":"928569","bookVersion":2042128132,"chapterUid":7,"content":"先看历史发展，理解怎么来的","friendship":0,"htmlContent":"","isPrivate":0,"range":"1846-1909","title":"","type":1,"reviewId":"9949958_7fRjzU1PH","userVid":9949958,"topics":[],"createTime":1584233308,"flag":0,"isLike":0,"isReposted":0,"book":{"bookId":"928569","format":"epub","version":465933926,"soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"type":0,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/61/YueWen_928569/s_YueWen_928569.jpg","title":"买入，持有，富有：一名金牛基金经理的投资之路","author":"张可兴","payType":1048577},"chapterIdx":7,"chapterTitle":"二级市场的引路人是巴菲特","author":{"userVid":9949958,"name":"孙大年","avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/0u8VlNPjial6zuBqSazyIoM4KHl1W5mYMTMFVibJ387ia62l40PaCryL953jkW76HxzUkloyqTZ1h7VQdobMTgtmf26uLTTSkXR2WWAKuINauU/132","isFollowing":1,"isFollower":1,"isBlacking":0,"isBlackBy":0,"isHide":1,"isV":0,"roleTags":[],"followPromote":"","isDeepV":false,"deepVTitle":"","signature":"","medalInfo":{"id":"M3-0-2000","desc":"阅读天数","title":"阅读天数","levelIndex":2000}}}},{"reviewId":"9949958_7fRjwXvUc","review":{"abstract":"有了“道”之后，要想持续成功还需要“术”。投资是困难的，不是你懂了价值投资或“买股票就是买企业的股权”这句话就可以赚钱，你还需要具备把事情做对的能力：找到优秀的企业并看准它未来的发展蓝图。对商业规律的把握，对企业估值的判断，对市场规律的认知，都需要不断地学习和积累。其实这个过程就是你学习如何“把事情做正确”，唯有这样，坚持在自己的能力圈范围之内，犯错的概率才会下降很多！","atUserVids":[],"bookId":"928569","bookVersion":2042128132,"chapterUid":7,"content":"道术法？\n市场表现和经营成绩不分彼此。\n商业洞察，市场理解。","friendship":0,"htmlContent":"","isPrivate":0,"range":"1616-1802","title":"","type":1,"reviewId":"9949958_7fRjwXvUc","userVid":9949958,"topics":[],"createTime":1584233264,"flag":0,"isLike":0,"isReposted":0,"book":{"bookId":"928569","format":"epub","version":465933926,"soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"type":0,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/61/YueWen_928569/s_YueWen_928569.jpg","title":"买入，持有，富有：一名金牛基金经理的投资之路","author":"张可兴","payType":1048577},"chapterIdx":7,"chapterTitle":"二级市场的引路人是巴菲特","author":{"userVid":9949958,"name":"孙大年","avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/0u8VlNPjial6zuBqSazyIoM4KHl1W5mYMTMFVibJ387ia62l40PaCryL953jkW76HxzUkloyqTZ1h7VQdobMTgtmf26uLTTSkXR2WWAKuINauU/132","isFollowing":1,"isFollower":1,"isBlacking":0,"isBlackBy":0,"isHide":1,"isV":0,"roleTags":[],"followPromote":"","isDeepV":false,"deepVTitle":"","signature":"","medalInfo":{"id":"M3-0-2000","desc":"阅读天数","title":"阅读天数","levelIndex":2000}}}},{"reviewId":"9949958_7fRhIlVGR","review":{"abstract":"2001年我在北京新东方参加雅思培训，感受到了新东方强大的市场影响力，很多班级都是几百人上千人的课堂，非常火爆。当时我想自己能不能搞一个这样的培训班。我首先考虑的是能不能干过新东方，调研发现在北京干不过，那么就换个地方，去西安。西安当时没有新东方分校，只有一些私人的小作坊级别的辅导班，我经过两三个月的观察认为自己干，完全能干赢他们。为什么这么说？你去看小作坊的运作思路、市场营销，就会有这个自信。当时我们并没有做教育培训的经验，但也没觉得这事做不了，好像不是很复杂，没有经验就去复制模仿，你只需要比当地市场第一名做得更好就行。这些小作坊后来一打就垮，这也印证了我对教育培训行业竞争方式的判断，即只要你成本更低、效果更好，就更有竞争优势。","atUserVids":[],"bookId":"928569","bookVersion":2042128132,"chapterUid":6,"content":"商业洞察","friendship":0,"htmlContent":"","isPrivate":0,"range":"1114-1433","title":"","type":1,"reviewId":"9949958_7fRhIlVGR","userVid":9949958,"topics":[],"createTime":1584231600,"flag":0,"isLike":0,"isReposted":0,"book":{"bookId":"928569","format":"epub","version":465933926,"soldout":0,"bookStatus":1,"type":0,"cover":"https://cdn.weread.qq.com/weread/cover/61/YueWen_928569/s_YueWen_928569.jpg","title":"买入，持有，富有：一名金牛基金经理的投资之路","author":"张可兴","payType":1048577},"chapterIdx":6,"chapterTitle":"我的创业之路","author":{"userVid":9949958,"name":"孙大年","avatar":"https://thirdwx.qlogo.cn/mmopen/vi_32/0u8VlNPji